formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. This certificate is being issued for RERA compliance for the Entity (Harsiddh Infra - East Ebony) and is based on the records and documents produced before me and explanations provided to me by the management of the Entity; based on the review of unaudited books of accounts till December 31, 2022.
2. As on 31.12.2022, unsecured loan as per books of accounts were Rs. 167 Lakh and loan and advances were Rs. 150 lakhs. As a result, actual utilisation of unsecured loans towards the project was Rs. 17 lakhs only. It was not possible for us to identify and verify as to out of total unsecured loan, which unsecured loan was utilised for project and which unsecured loan was given as loans and advance and therefore, we have mentioned the details of all secured and unsecured loans availed in the legal entity.
3. KYC Details of allotees such as mobile number, ID number etc. as provided by the promoter has not been verified by us.
4.The promoters have not shared copies of agreement for sale, in absence of which, date of agreement have not been mentioned in Form 3.
5. As per unaudited books of accounts, project expenditure incurred and paid till 31.12.2022 is Rs. 648533074, but In RERA Form-3, the system has captured the total project expenses to the extent of estimates.
